<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>~2pm Saturday EST ~ 11am Saturday PST ~ 5pm Saturday London ~ 6 am Sunday Sydney~</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
The faire will be held in the hidden valley of the Dreadlands right near the Luclin spire (which should be safe for all ages).  Wizards can teleport you straight there, else simply catch the Kunark spire from the Nexus.<br>
<br>
The channel for organization will be LOSLANGUAGE, please join it when you arrive and let it be known whether you seek to teach or learn, and which tongues interest you.<br>
<br>
Those of dubious morals (ie, lightbringers and palerot) should not expect to be welcomed with open arms.  Those following the dark paths are invited to come and exchange tongues with those of like mind and religion.<br>
